node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Blind Skateboards on July 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, outdoors, tree and text that says 'CLEAN MANUFACTURING PLANTING BACK GIVING TREES FOR REGROWTH SUSTAINABILITY LABOR EACH HARVESTED MISSION FAIR'.

node.text: This week is #NationalForestWeek, an annual celebration of the National Forests! As part of our Regrowth Sustainability Mission, we plant 1 tree for every tree we use to make skateboards. In support of National Forest Week we will be doubling our donation to National Forest Foundation to plant twice as many trees for every deck sold on ThankYouSupply.com @nationalforest #RegrowthSkateboards #NationalForestWeek
